            <div class="bg-navy-900 border-2 border-slate-200  p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 uppercase">WHY AJAX NEEDS WATERPROOFING</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-300">
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Lake sediment clay creates high foundation pressure</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
